full_text: From @WSJopinion: John Durham’s indictments have turned any number of narratives on their heads, including the question of which 2016 presidential campaign was in bed with Russians. It wasn’t Donald Trump’s, writes @KimStrassel https://t.co/I7cAU2Omhi
